Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SURVIVORS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:55.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,TOWN OF POLTOS, ROMOS KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everyone run!\N-Run! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The town of Poltos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my lack of manners,\Nbut there is no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I bring news from Queen Flora\Nof Carl Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this place a little too cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army's been rampaging\Nall over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught some fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is the real Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Such impressive destructive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban truly is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, if it isn't my master,\NDark Commander Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at that crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Zaboera, am truly in awe of\NKing Ban's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And he even granted me the position\Nof Dark Army Second-in-Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I cut ties with\Nthat fool Hadorra when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you converted Hadorra\Ninto a Superior Being,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,did you not notice the Black Core\Nimplanted in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I noticed it. But I left it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured he'd die\Nfor King Ban eventually anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and so long as I wasn't\Ncaught in the blast, it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not worthy to speak ill of Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognize your part\Nin saving King Ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will never trust gutter rats\Nwho care only for their own success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They always turn on their masters\Nwhen it suits their needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do,\NI won't hesitate to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Say whatever you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength is not about possessing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about being the last one standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll find a way\Nto have the last laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I wash up here?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You swam all this way\Nwhile carrying me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You never cease to amaze me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Grisly?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without my Magic Power this is bad!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have to protect her at all costs!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over here!\NI'll take you down even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You found them, Troop Number Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You morons. Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!\NWe'll take you to the Forest Fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job finding them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Forest Fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were rescued by the Order of Carl.\NWe're stationed there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of Carl survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as Queen Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's been four days.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army has been using\Ntheir flying Dark Citadel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to drop bombs all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,On one target every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I wondered why\Nthey weren't attacking capitals,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but after hearing your accounts,\Nnow I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King wants to destroy\Nthe Surface World, not invade it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least you two made it back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Dai, Hyunckel,\Nand Crocodine also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Holy Mother Dragon\Ntook Dai away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel and Big Guy took a direct hit\Nfrom the Dark King's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hadorra hadn't shown up,\Nme and Maam and Gome would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We got our butts kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp and Maam have both felt\Nthe terror of the Dark King up close.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing we can say\Nto lift their spirits.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... there's nothing we can do\Nto stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both Disciples of Aban,\Nare you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Then this person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. She escaped the fall\Nof Carl with a handful of knights
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and has been waiting for a chance\Nto strike back at the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She brought us here to this fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp. Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you really carry on\Nthe will of Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you mustn't voice such weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know Master Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban was a member of our Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He risked his life to protect us\Nwith the lead knight, Roka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. With your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when Hadorra led his forces\Non an attack on our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my father fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As princess, I had to lead my army\Nto fight against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To boost my subjects' morale,\NI had to put on a strong face.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I was unsure if we really could fight\Nthe supernatural powers of the Dark Lord.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was terrified.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't just me.\NEveryone in the palace was scared.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! There's no way\Nwe can beat the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, we'll gain nothing\Nby scampering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when Aban spoke up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Non, non, non!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do nothing\Nthen we really will gain nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If all we can do is scamper around\Nthen our course is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends, let us scamper around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I broke out into laughter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, in front of everyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I realized...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this man is a natural-born Hero\Nwho can give everyone hope.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why\Nwhenever I find myself losing hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicate myself to\Nscampering around as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe in what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. He's dead, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were alive somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he would never stand still\Nand let his home be ravaged as it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he would save us if he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it. She...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was in love with Master Aban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like... to scamper around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I can't be Master Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Though incompetent, I am his student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now is not the time. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Recuperate your strength for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a great woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something reassuring...\Nalmost overpowering about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why\Nyou respect her so much, Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So she and Master Aban were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a sort of\Nmature allure to her that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You lech!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona! Come to the command room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army is moving against Ringaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.48,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}CASTLING{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.49,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEALING-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How boring it is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for things go so smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree wholeheartedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An unfortunate card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This card comes up every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying those\Nwho would resist me are still out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it means,\Nit's definitely trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been wrong with my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us draw them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have those two held captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,TERAN KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty! Outside! Look in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Mother Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in Teran, where we worship\Nthe God of Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the life of a Dragon Knight\Nis coming to an end right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I... make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. You have died.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Holy Mother Dragon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I preside over the life and death of\NDragon Knights as a servant of the gods.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Mother Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Dragon Knight dies,\Nto pass on the power of the Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a legendary Dragon appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have taken an astral form\Nand have merged with me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon your soul shall be led\Nto the world of the gods.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a new Dragon Knight\Nis going to replace me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There will be no new Dragon Knight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are the last Knight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gods of Humans, Darklings, and Dragons\Ncreated the Dragon Knights{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to defeat any evil that would\Ntip the balance of the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But over a long, long time,\Nthe power of such evil has grown.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark King Ban possesses a power\Ngreater than a god.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with a Dragon Knight's power,\Nevil can no longer be punished.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, overcoming the Dragon Knights{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}may be what drove evil\Nto become so powerful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is why I am ending\Nthe history of the Dragon Knights.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer have the power\Nto birth a new Knight anyway.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dark force is bringing\Nmy life to an end.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there won't be anyone\Nwho can stop Dark King Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can forget your trying battles now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your soul can return\Nto the heavens with me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's wrong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have two souls.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the true last Knight, Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy, Dai, was born between myself\Nand a human woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The death you sensed was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! That's not possible!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy's life has not yet ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I ask that you grant this boy\None more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one can defeat the Dark King,\Nno matter how powerful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I resurrect him,\Nhe will only face a cruel hell again.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy has a power\Nno normal Dragon Knight has.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something beyond power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Knights can only last\Nfor one generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could a Dragon Knight sire a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods must have sensed the limits of\Nthe Dragon Knights and gave us this hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world where power\Nrules over everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,he can defeat evil with his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that is why the gods\Nallowed this boy to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shall grant the very last\Nof my power to Dai.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you will write\Nthe history of the Dragon Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,raising a child with the woman you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do so, you must defeat Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not strong like you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Soara and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will always be with you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fetch someone who can use Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him to Queen Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... for being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai is asleep.\NHis wounds have been healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid I have some very bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A message from the Dark Army\Nwas sent to countries across the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,using a communication spell with mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the translated message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the foolish humans of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a few days, our Dark Army{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shall vaporize this Surface World\Nwhere you dwell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have no way of stopping us.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Accept this as fate\Nand die with your world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To celebrate this grand achievement,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the traitors who aided\Nthe defeated Hero and his party,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel the Dark Swordsman and\NBeast King Crocodine, shall be executed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those interested may witness this\Nas a memory to take to the afterlife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They die at noon in two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the northern mountains of Carl Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Executed?! The bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hyunckel and Crocodine\Nare being held by the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have a meeting at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:12.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:18.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:29.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:35.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:41.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:47.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:53.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:59.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:16.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:22.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:25.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:30.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The missing Hyunckel and Crocodine\Nare being held by the Dark Army.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Dai has returned after\Nparting with his father, Baran.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While Dai's wounds have healed, memories\Nof his defeat by Ban torment him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, Popp and the others\Nbelieve that Dai will stand once more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dai and Popp"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
